{{Infobox language |name = Pasé |states = |region = |extinct = ? |familycolor = American |fam1 = [[Maipurean languages|Arawakan]] |fam2 = Northern |fam3 = [[Upper Amazon Arawakan|Upper Amazonian]] |fam4 = (unclassified) |iso3 = none |linglist = qoj |glotto=pass1250 |glottorefname= Passe }}
'''Pasé''' (Passe) is an extinct, poorly attested, and unclassified [[Arawakan language]]. Kaufman (1994) placed it in his Río Negro branch, but this is not followed in Aikhenvald (1999).
